name: what-is-it-really-used-for
title: What is it really used for?
author: Mr Doomah, Coppermine
description: A tool to help you find out where items and fluids come from and where they are used.  This is a fork of the original 'What is it used for?' by Mr Doomah, updated for newer Factorio versions and with additional features.  Russian translation by Schmarotzer.  Japanese translation by shiru_tan and shela.  Some graphical elements based on Helmod, by Helfima.
